Powershell commands to wnload terraform

Here are the complete PowerShell commands to download and install Terraform v1.14.0:

# Create terraform directory
New-Item -ItemType Directory -Force -Path "C:\terraform"

# Download Terraform v1.14.0
Invoke-WebRequest -Uri "https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/1.14.0/terraform_1.14.0_windows_amd64.zip" -OutFile "C:\terraform\terraform.zip"

# Extract the zip file
Expand-Archive -Path "C:\terraform\terraform.zip" -DestinationPath "C:\terraform" -Force

# Remove zip file
Remove-Item "C:\terraform\terraform.zip"

# Add to PATH permanently
$currentPath = [Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable("PATH", [EnvironmentVariableTarget]::User)
if ($currentPath -notlike "*C:\terraform*") {
    [Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable("PATH", $currentPath + ";C:\terraform", [EnvironmentVariableTarget]::User)
}

# Refresh PATH for current session
$env:PATH = [Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable("PATH", [EnvironmentVariableTarget]::User)

Copy
powershell
After running these commands, restart your PowerShell/Command Prompt and verify:

terraform version

